➜成都逛街众生相
http://www.sohu.com/a/422724465_115837	20672
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201005/1fbd0b4c37024948877356e6cd4baabd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">前段时间，成都太古里的街拍火到了外网。推特上一位博主随手转发一条来自TikTok的街拍视频，就收获了3000万观看量和百万点赞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201005/40d2f7a77d484c2fafb2f4cb5b745ee2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">评论区对Chinese Street Fashion的讨论也很热烈↓↓↓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201005/4890424453624d65bec816bd5be50819.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
